            "heading": "LOS ANGELES, CA, June 1st, 2025",
            "body": "<p>This is not a collaboration, it’s a partnership between two veteran designers; Amin; specializing in leather & denim for 12 years, and Paul Kaufman; a legendary shoemaker who introduced the iconic brand, Dr. Martens, to the United States in 1980.<br/><br/></p>",
